@zfha 是自己运行的incubator-weex>ios>playground 的工程，真机使用调试工具的时候，weexplayground 老是崩溃
浏览器上显示“Warning:The session with native was closed,please restart your native app!“

`#pragma mark Thread Management

- (void)_runLoopThread
{
    [[NSRunLoop currentRunLoop] addPort:[NSMachPort port] forMode:NSDefaultRunLoopMode];
    
    while (!_stopRunning) {
        @autoreleasepool {
            [[NSRunLoop currentRunLoop] runMode:NSDefaultRunLoopMode beforeDate:[NSDate distantFuture]]; // 崩在这 行
        }
    }
}`

@zfha 是WXDevtool 版本问题
Installing WXDevtool 0.9.5 (was 0.8.2)
podfile 改一下就好了
